	Additionally the App installs a collector for UCS specific metrics like UCS version and role.
	</p>
	<p>
	The &quot;UCS Dashboard Client&quot; App needs to be installed on all UCS servers which should be available in the &quot;UCS Dashboard&quot; App. The &quot;UCS Dashboard&quot; App itself needs to installed on one of the UCS servers.
	</p>
